<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="truly-adv">truly <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'truːli/    美 /'truːli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>真诚地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’m truly sorry that things had to end like this. 
事情落到这样的结局，我真的很抱歉。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>确实；确切：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>That painting is truly beautiful! 
那幅画真是漂亮！</p><footer>北师大⑥ – 17</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>In theatres and teahouses you can experience a truly Chinese way of life.
在剧院和茶馆，你可以感受到真正的中国生活方式。</p><footer>2009 全国书面表达改</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="yours-truly">Yours truly</h3>
<p>1.<strong>[用于书信结尾、签名之前] 你忠实的</strong>  </p></div>